1.2.0 2026xxxx
CR: Build: Reorganization of the release process
    - 1.x javax.servlet
    - 2.x jakarta.servlet
    The major number of project version is no longer tied to future Servlet API
    major versions to avoid ambiguity once newer Servlet API releases become
    available.

